    • UserProfile

      public UserProfile(String deviceID, String name, String email, String phoneNumber, String pictureURL, String facilityURL, boolean allowNotifications, List<String> notificationsArray, List<String> joinedEvents, boolean isOrganizer, boolean isAdmin)
      Complete UserProfile Constructor
      Parameters:
      deviceID - Unique id of user's device
      name - String name of the user
      email - String email of the user
      phoneNumber - String representation of user's phone number
      pictureURL - String URL representation holds user's image information
      facilityURL - String URL representation holds facility image information
      allowNotifications - Boolean keeping track of whether the user allows notifications
      notificationsArray - List keeping track of user's notifications
      joinedEvents - List of events the user has joined, events represented by their String id
      isOrganizer - Boolean keeping track whether ths user is an organizer
      isAdmin - Boolean keeping track whether the user is an admin
